---
import SplitLineHeading from '../ui/SplitLineHeading.astro';
---

<section class="py-16 lg:py-24" data-animate="fade-in-from-bottom">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <SplitLineHeading
      lines={['WELCOME TO PRAIANO,', 'THE HEART OF THE AMALFI COAST!']}
      tag="h2"
      class="text-center mb-12 uppercase"
    />

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-muted leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>
          Praiano is a small fisherman village perched on the cliffs between Amalfi and Positano.
          From here you can see the legendary Li Galli islands, once home to Rudolf Nureyev.
          Unlike its more famous neighbours, Praiano offers a quieter, more authentic experience
          of the Amalfi Coast — with breathtaking views, hidden beaches, and a warm community
          that welcomes visitors like family.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-muted leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>
          Just around the corner you can catch a boat to Capri and its famous Faraglioni rocks,
          or stroll down to Positano. The narrow alleys of Praiano are adorned with ceramic
          installations — tiles, murals, and decorative panels that tell stories of the sea,
          the sun, and centuries of craftsmanship. Every corner is a discovery, and every
          ceramic piece carries the soul of this magical place.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
